{"id":567540,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/09/【立此存照】外交部要求韩国停止萨德-评论大型车/","date":"2017-09-07T08:00:39Z","modified":"2017-09-07T08:02:38Z","title":"【立此存照】外交部要求韩国停止萨德 评论大型车祸现场","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>@头条新闻 近日发布的一则关于中国外交部要求韩国停止部署萨德的微博，很快就引来大量不买账的网民，评论内容几乎一面倒地表示了对中国对朝政策的不满和对韩国的同情。新浪微博后来关闭并清空了评论及转发内容。</p>\n<p>朝鲜近期成功测试氢弹后，中国气象局于9月3日启动了<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/169403281_117884\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">突发核生化环境污染事件气象保障应急响应</a>。近在咫尺的核威胁，让越来越多的中国民众开始理解韩国坚持部署萨德的理由。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_567544\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/头条新闻-萨德.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-567544\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/头条新闻-萨德.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/头条新闻-萨德.jpg 1334w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/头条新闻-萨德-300x204.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/头条新闻-萨德-768x522.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/头条新闻-萨德-1024x695.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">评论内容被清空，转发内容也无法显示；微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>以下图片来自新浪微博 <a href=\"http://weibo.com/234278582\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@只配炸杠</a>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjav9ci913j30qo76fkio.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567541\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjav9ci913j30qo76fkio.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"4845\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjav9ci913j30qo76fkio.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjav9ci913j30qo76fkio-31x300.jpg 31w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjav9ci913j30qo76fkio-768x7442.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjarwdxsw6j30p87ps7wj.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-567543\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjarwdxsw6j30p87ps7wj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"5507\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjarwdxsw6j30p87ps7wj.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/005KpIGdgy1fjarwdxsw6j30p87ps7wj-93x1024.jpg 93w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,27949],"tags":[18808,9980,26448,22250,20895]}